{"title":"I Am Learning To Abandon the World","author":{"name":"Linda Pastan"},"publishDate":"2011-05-08","lines":[{"line":"I am learning to abandon the world","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"before it can abandon me.","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"Already I have given up the moon","stanza":1,"number":3},{"line":"and snow, closing my shades","stanza":1,"number":4},{"line":"against the claims of white.","stanza":1,"number":5},{"line":"And the world has taken","stanza":1,"number":6},{"line":"my father, my friends.","stanza":1,"number":7},{"line":"I have given up melodic lines of hills,","stanza":1,"number":8},{"line":"moving to a flat, tuneless landscape.","stanza":1,"number":9},{"line":"And every night I give my body up","stanza":1,"number":10},{"line":"limb by limb, working upwards","stanza":1,"number":11},{"line":"across bone, towards the heart.","stanza":1,"number":12},{"line":"But morning comes with small","stanza":1,"number":13},{"line":"reprieves of coffee and birdsong.","stanza":1,"number":14},{"line":"A tree outside the window","stanza":1,"number":15},{"line":"which was simply shadow moments ago","stanza":1,"number":16},{"line":"takes back its branches twig","stanza":1,"number":17},{"line":"by leafy twig.","stanza":1,"number":18},{"line":"And as I take my body back","stanza":1,"number":19},{"line":"the sun lays its warm muzzle on my lap","stanza":1,"number":20},{"line":"as if to make amends.","stanza":1,"number":21}]}